# Fanqie Novel AI Video Drama Batch Generator

## Features
- Auto split multi-chapter novel into episodes
- Generate AI manhua / digital human video
- Auto voiceover, subtitle, cover, title, tags
- Batch output for Douyin/ Kuaishou/ Fanqie series

## Input
- Multi-chapter novel text
- type: manhua / zhenren
- style: xufu / ancient / modern / fantasy

## Output
- final_video.mp4
- cover.jpg
- info.json
- script.md
